=Episode 9=

2
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:07,220
(Candlelight Proposal
Is a Blessing or a Curse)

3
00:00:08,780 --> 00:00:10,580
Why are you so indifferent
to Ye Zhongjue?

4
00:00:10,660 --> 00:00:11,980
If I were him,
I would have ignored you long ago.

5
00:00:12,660 --> 00:00:14,380
I'm playing hard to get with him.

6
00:00:14,940 --> 00:00:16,780
Men's enthusiasm is time-limited.

7
00:00:17,020 --> 00:00:18,300
You should make sure
it's under your control.

8
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:19,220
If you go too far,

9
00:00:19,220 --> 00:00:20,300
he won't be interested in you.

10
00:00:20,940 --> 00:00:22,860
Everything is under my control so far.

11
00:00:23,940 --> 00:00:25,700
What's going on, Mo Suqing?

12
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:27,100
I've known you for over a decade,

13
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:28,940
but I didn't notice
that you are so attractive.

14
00:00:29,900 --> 00:00:30,860
Neither did I.

15
00:00:49,540 --> 00:00:50,180
Say something!

16
00:00:54,340 --> 00:00:55,220
Are you pretending to be dumb?

17
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:57,700
Are you telling me or not?

18
00:00:59,460 --> 00:01:00,180
Tell me!

19
00:01:02,140 --> 00:01:03,140
Say something!

20
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:04,300
Say!

21
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:06,820
Still pretending, huh?

22
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:09,180
Say something!

23
00:01:10,980 --> 00:01:11,660
I'll starve you

24
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:12,620
until you speak.

25
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:14,950
=Trick in Love=

26
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:19,060
(Adapted from the novel
"Mr. Intrigue's Love Game" by Yun Qi Mo Li)

27
00:01:28,180 --> 00:01:29,540
Are you dumb?

28
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:34,540
