72
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:30,940
But I'm not forcing you to marry me.

73
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,420
If you are not saying yes today,

74
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:36,340
I will ask you tomorrow.

75
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:38,220
If you don't agree tomorrow,

76
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:40,180
I'll wait for the day after tomorrow.

77
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:43,580
As long as you don't leave me,

78
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:45,780
even if I have to wait till old,

79
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:46,780
I will...

80
